# Keep the build context small and NEVER ship secrets or local junk into images.

# Dependencies / build outputs (reinstalled / rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/out
**/target

# Secrets & local env — config is injected at runtime via platform secrets.
# (.env.example is intentionally kept so the template ships.)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# VCS / CI / editor
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea

# Logs & OS files
*.log
**/*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Docs & misc not needed at runtime
docs
*.md
!apps/api/**/*.md
